	DESC:You can check the box that precedes this boon to purchase a suit of dragonhide armor or dragonhide shield made out of crag linnorm scales, reducing its price by up to 500 gp (minimum cost 0 gp). Crag linnormhide armor is immune to fire damage. Alternatively, you can check the box to convert any dragonhide armor you have into crag linnormhide armor at no cost. Any discounted energy resistance abilities the armor may grant change to grant fire resistance instead of their original type.

Personal Guard (Sovereign Court Faction)
	KEY:PFS Scenario 9-11 ~ Personal Guard
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:Chronicle_S09-11.PFSBoon
	VISIBLE:YES
	COST:0
	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Background,Sovereign Court Faction
	DESC:You have earned the service of a loyal Ulfen bodyguard who accompanies you on your adventures. This character functions as a follower vanity (Pathfinder Campaign Setting: Pathfinder Society Field Guide 60), not taking any space on the battlefield or otherwise serving as a combatant. The bodyguard grants you a constant +1 bonus to your AC against attack rolls to confirm critical hits. If you would take damage from a critical hit or sneak attack, you can choose for your bodyguard to absorb 20 points of damage from the attack, though this kills the follower. You can spend 4 Prestige Points between adventures to recruit a new bodyguard.

